sources.title: Valentine DayZ (Full Movie) 2018, Horror, Zombies
sources.description:
Middle-aged Max and Sara meet and fall for each other in Palm Springs, but their love story is cut short due to a sudden zombie outbreak which reveals sides to both of them the other had not seen before.

Directed by Mark Allen Michaels
2018
Starring Dallas Valdez, Carrie Keagan, Robert Allen Mukes
